sentences: After the band broke up in 2003, he recorded his debut solo album, American Hearts, in a barn near his home Palenville, New York.
The album, released in 2007, marked a shift in musical direction towards a more traditional and minimalist folk sound, with Bondy playing mostly acoustic guitar and harmonica.
His second album, When the Devil's Loose, was recorded in Mississippi and released in September 2009.
Bondy released his third album, Believers, on September 13, 2011.
Bondy released his fourth album, Enderness, on May 10, 2019.
was featured in season four of the television series Friday Night Lights and was included on the Friday Night Lights Vol. 2 soundtrack.
